    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>SEAT BELT LAW</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By KAREN DeMASTERS</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Demasters, Karen</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>New Jersey State Police begin handing out leaflets at toll plazas warning drivers that they can be ticketed for not wearing seat belts without first being stopped for other offenses (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>During the first week in May, State Police have been handing out leaflets at roadway toll plazas warning drivers that they can also hand out tickets for not wearing seat belts. As of last Monday, the police in New Jersey have the right to ticket motorists for not wearing seat belts without first stopping them on suspicion of another motor vehicle offense.</p>
        <p>KAREN DeMASTERS</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>During the first week in May, State Police have been handing out leaflets at roadway toll plazas warning drivers that they can also hand out tickets for not wearing seat belts. As of last Monday, the police in New Jersey have the right to ticket motorists for not wearing seat belts without first stopping them on suspicion of another motor vehicle offense.</p>
        <p>KAREN DeMASTERS</p>
